  "texts": [
    "With the increasing availability of health data and the advancement of DL techniques, personalized healthcare monitoring can potentially transform how we manage our health.",
    "Real-time diagnosis and treatment planningReal-time diagnosis and treatment planning is a critical aspect of healthcare that can benefit greatly from DL and IoT-based bio-and medical informatics.",
    "DL models can be trained on large datasets of medical images and patient records to provide a real-time diagnosis.",
    "These models can be deployed on IoT-enabled devices to provide immediate feedback to healthcare providers.",
    "This can be particularly useful in emergencies where quick diagnosis is critical."
  ],
